      m_Calls: []
  m_text: '1. Pour 100 mL of 6% Hydrogen Peroxide (H2O2) into the flask.


    2.
    Grab 1 tablespoon of dish soap with spoon and pour into flask.


    3. Swirl
    the flask for 2 seconds.


    4. Add the sachet of dry yeast to the empty cup.


    5.
    Add 4 tablespoons of water to the cup.


    6. Stir the cup and mix it for 30
    seconds.


    7. Pour the cup mixture into the flask.'
